# Playwright Testing — Multi-Repo Source Routing

Rule ini aktif **hanya** untuk tugas Playwright: menulis/menjalankan spec, crawling UI, investigasi selector, mapping TC → automation, debug E2E.

Untuk pertanyaan QA umum, analisis requirement, atau Jira card → tetap **`olshoperp-docs` saja** (lihat `02-repo-context`, `10-anti-hallucination`, `12-jira-card-format`).

Standar eksekusi run, retry, auth: `14-playwright-e2e.mdc`.

---

## Repo & path

Asumsi tiga repo sebagai **sibling** di folder GitHub yang sama:

| Repo | Path relatif dari `olshoperp-docs` | Peran |
|------|-------------------------------------|-------|
| **olshoperp-docs** (workspace ini) | `.` | Requirement, TC, expected result, manifest |
| **olshoperp** | `../olshoperp` | Backend — API, controller, job, validasi server |
| **olshoperp-frontend** | `../olshoperp-frontend` | Frontend — komponen UI, selector, route FE, folder `e2e/` |

Jika path sibling tidak ada, laporkan ke user — jangan tebak lokasi repo.

---

## Matriks sumber baca (khusus Playwright)

| Kebutuhan | Sumber utama | Bukan dari |
|-----------|--------------|------------|
| Expected result, langkah TC, precondition | `qa-docs/{slug}/requirement.md`, `qa-docs/{slug}/test-cases/TC-*.md` | Infer hanya dari kode app |
| Slug menu, `menu_name`, route staging | `qa-docs/_meta/manifest.yaml` | Tebak dari URL FE saja |
| Selector, label UI, struktur halaman | `olshoperp-frontend` (`src/`, `e2e/helpers/`) | Docs atau asumsi umum |
| Endpoint API, payload, response, validasi server | `olshoperp` (routes, controllers, jobs) | Field `code_globs` manifest tanpa baca file |
| Sidebar crawl / navigasi menu | `olshoperp-frontend` + `qa-docs/sidebar-menu/` | — |

Prioritas requirement tetap: `requirement.md` > `knowledge-base.md` > `technical.md` — sama seperti persona QA (`05-qa-engineer-persona`).

---

## Lokasi kode Playwright per repo

| Repo | Folder automation | Kapan dipakai |
|------|-------------------|---------------|
| `olshoperp-docs` | `tests/` | TC-driven automation dari qa-docs; sidebar crawler |
| `olshoperp-frontend` | `e2e/` | Regression staging; spec terhubung Test Case Library |

Sebelum menulis atau mengubah spec: baca TC terkait (`automated_spec`, README `test-cases/`) — tentukan repo target yang benar.

---

## Larangan scope bleed

| Konteks | Boleh baca repo app? | AS-IS requirement dari mana? |
|---------|----------------------|------------------------------|
| Playwright / crawler / automation | ✅ `olshoperp` + `olshoperp-frontend` | **`olshoperp-docs`** (TC + requirement) |
| Jawaban QA umum | ❌ — docs only (`10-anti-hallucination`) | **`olshoperp-docs`** |
| Jira Bug / Improvement / CR | ❌ untuk Expected & AS-IS bisnis | **`olshoperp-docs`** (`12-jira-card-format`) |

- Temuan dari kode atau run Playwright **bukan** pengganti requirement — label **Catatan automation (dari kode/run)** jika perlu disebutkan.
- Actual ≠ requirement di run E2E → laporkan sebagai potential doc gap atau bug candidate; **jangan** update docs otomatis (`03-qa-docs-immutable`).

---

## Jira card — docs tetap referensi utama

Meski investigasi Playwright memakai `olshoperp` / `olshoperp-frontend`:

- **Expected Result** / **Expected Improvement** / **New Requirement (TO-BE)** → validasi dari `qa-docs/{slug}/requirement.md`
- **Actual Result** → boleh dari output Playwright (error UI, HTTP status, screenshot path)
- Detail teknis (nama controller, selector, spec path) → **Additional Context** saja, bukan section utama card

Lihat validasi Expected di `12-jira-card-format.mdc`.

---

## Workflow Playwright (ringkas)

1. Resolve `{menu-slug}` via `manifest.yaml` (`olshoperp-docs`)
2. Baca TC + `requirement.md` — steps & expected result adalah hukum (`14` §1)
3. Baca `olshoperp-frontend` untuk selector/UI; `olshoperp` jika TC menyentuh API atau validasi server
4. Tulis/jalankan spec di repo target (`tests/` atau `e2e/`) per `14-playwright-e2e.mdc`
5. Laporkan PASS/FAIL **terhadap expected dari TC/requirement**, bukan terhadap perilaku kode semata

